    "Table 4.2: Algorithm trend word count relevance GCN 52 1 Random Forest 41 0.93 Logistic Regression 28 0.66 GAT 19 0.42 MLP 13 0.31 Random Forest is another popular choice due to its ability to handle both classification and regression tasks, as well as its robustness against overfitting.",
